## Key Outcomes

- Successfully downloaded and loaded the HDI dataset.
- Verified the dataset structure and dimensions.
- Explored feature names, data types, and statistical properties.
- Visualized relationships between education, life expectancy, and HDI.
- Identified highly correlated features using a correlation heatmap.
- Prepared the dataset for preprocessing and Linear Regression model training.

---

## Result

Epic 3 was successfully completed by acquiring, understanding, and analyzing the Human Development Index dataset. The exploratory analysis provided valuable insights into the dataset and established a strong foundation for the next phase of data preprocessing and machine learning model development.
